      "span_text": "They need to recapitulate the mechanism triggering the disorder, such as a gene mutation (construct validity), reproduce the symptoms (biochemical, histological, behavioral) of the disorder (face validity), and respond to pharmacological interventions as humans would (predictive validity).   Defining to what extent an animal model of ASD is valid has been difficult."
